---
layout: default
subject: Reset Your Password
---
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1f2937; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hello {{user_name}},</p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
	We received a request to reset the password for your {{instance_name}} account.
	If you did not make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<!-- CTA Button -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 30px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="text-align: center;">
			<a href="{{reset_link}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #e98a54; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 36px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Reset Password</a>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin: 15px 0; word-break: break-all;">
	Or copy this link: <a href="{{reset_link}}" style="color: #e98a54;">{{reset_link}}</a>
</p>

<!-- Warning Box -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 20px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="background-color: #fef3e6; border: 1px solid #f8d4b0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px;">
			<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9a4d1c; margin: 0;">
				<strong>Security Notice:</strong> This reset link will expire in {{expire_hours}} hours.
				Do not share this link with anyone.
			</p>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
	If you continue to have problems, please contact your instance administrator.
</p>
